# EXISTING STRUCTURES

# ERROR TIPS
### Errors when using extracting but the furnace has no ingredients
 -  Make sure the furnace contains the item you are trying to extract before attempting to extract. The furnace has status EntityStatus.NO_INGREDIENTS.
### Errors when using extracting but being too far
 -  Make sure to move to the target entity where you want to extract from before extracting items
### Inventory full when harvesting
- Ensure your inventory has space before attempting to harvest items.
